  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Welsh Secretary writes to businesses about EU Transition
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The letter to hundreds of Welsh businesses focusses on readiness for the end of the EU Transition period. </p>

  </div>
</div>

